  ('social-worker-moex-05910', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '1950 年代美國學者戴明（E. Deming）提出學習自日本品質取向管理；到 1990 年代管理界費建邦（A. Feigenbaum）等人承襲品質管理概念，發展出全面品質管理（TQM），歸納了五大核心價值，下列那一 核心價值，較不屬於TQM？', '["以客為尊", "按件計酬", "持續改善", "團隊合作"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
